    <item>
      <title>内阁声明缓解担忧，南非市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/south-african-rand-rallies-as-godongwana-retains-finance-post</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 宣布新内阁并将优先考虑经济增长，结束了持续数周的不确定性，南非股市普遍上涨，表明投资者松了一口气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/south-african-rand-rallies-as-godongwana-retains-finance-post</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 07:09:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冲突升级，以色列军队遭真主党无人机袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/hezbollah-drone-wounds-18-israeli-troops-as-clashes-escalate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方称，真主党的无人机袭击造成 18 名士兵受伤，其中一人伤势严重，这是双方长期针锋相对的战事中的最新一次事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/hezbollah-drone-wounds-18-israeli-troops-as-clashes-escalate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 06:44:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎智英儿子称外国法官应退出香港法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/jimmy-lai-s-son-says-foreign-judges-should-quit-hong-kong-bench</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前媒体大亨黎智英的儿子呼吁所有外国法官离开香港的司法体系，给他们施加更大压力，迫使他们加入这股外逃大潮，这可能会削弱香港与中国内地之间的一个关键区别。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/jimmy-lai-s-son-says-foreign-judges-should-quit-hong-kong-bench</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 06:22:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙与法国左翼对手竞相阻止勒庞势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/macron-and-french-left-wing-rivals-race-to-stop-far-right-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的中间派联盟和左翼新人民阵线正在考虑是否将候选人从周日的第二轮立法选举中撤出，以阻止崛起的极右翼国民联盟掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/macron-and-french-left-wing-rivals-race-to-stop-far-right-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:49:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
